除刺杀其他海外哈马斯领导人的可能性。卢比奥重申，哈马斯作为武装组织不应再存在。","newsLink":"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20250915-%E5%8D%A2%E6%AF%94%E5%A5%A5%E4%B8%8E%E5%86%85%E5%A1%94%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E8%83%A1%E5%9C%A8%E8%80%B6%E8%B7%AF%E6%92%92%E5%86%B7%E4%BC%9A%E6%99%A4%E5%90%8E%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA-%E5%93%88%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E6%AD%A6%E8%A3%85%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%86%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8","thumbnail":"","detailImage":"news/detail/rfi/2025/09/15/1757954913000.webp","sourceId":"rfi"}]